      "text": "<h3 class=\"title-high\">Design and development updates</h3><p>The changelog acts as a historical record, detailing all the modifications made to the system's components, guidelines, and code. It records what, when, and where the change occurred across design and development.</p>   <h4 class=\"title-low\">Platforms</h4> <p>This changelog tracks updates across various platforms we use to build and maintain the design system. Look for changes to Figma files and GitLab repositories.</p>",
